    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO AVANTE! ATLANTIS</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/58de70496f9ed931057cdbe15710099d.poster.avif?t=1769509588\" width=1170 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/58de70496f9ed931057cdbe15710099d.webm?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/58de70496f9ed931057cdbe15710099d.mp4?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tactical turn-based adventure with the charm of a living board game. Command vibrant armies, uncover ancient truths, and fight for control of a world where every tile matters and every move carries weight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE STORY BEGINS → Atlantis Has Risen</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/ef5281d1bf40126e75ccfb726465967b.poster.avif?t=1769509588\" width=1170 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/ef5281d1bf40126e75ccfb726465967b.webm?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/ef5281d1bf40126e75ccfb726465967b.mp4?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >March across the reawakened island as the world's factions collide in the first <strong>Virtual War</strong>, each determined to claim Atlantis. Face rival commanders, outmaneuver their armies, and <strong>uncover the hidden forces</strong> that kept the island shrouded in <strong>mystery</strong> for centuries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WAYS TO PLAY → Choose Your Arena</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/dd88316d1b84bb280c52f152ed91bde3.poster.avif?t=1769509588\" width=1170 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/dd88316d1b84bb280c52f152ed91bde3.webm?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/dd88316d1b84bb280c52f152ed91bde3.mp4?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge the <strong>Computer</strong>, battle a <strong>friend locally</strong>, or <strong>play online</strong>: from <strong>quick fights</strong> you can slip into your day to <strong>longer encounters</strong> that unfold like a true battlefield campaign.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE DICE SYSTEM → Strategy With a Twist</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/529a7e803b5397e4dac359b383e0ac2e.poster.avif?t=1769509588\" width=1170 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/529a7e803b5397e4dac359b383e0ac2e.webm?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/529a7e803b5397e4dac359b383e0ac2e.mp4?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>custom D20</strong> and <strong>elemental D6, D4, and D8</strong> add small but meaningful swings to combat. Each roll nudges your unit's power, keeping battles dynamic without overshadowing strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE COMMANDERS → Characters With Attitude</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/a53ac989ce3ba1ecb6d283a57a2e91fc.poster.avif?t=1769509588\" width=1170 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/a53ac989ce3ba1ecb6d283a57a2e91fc.webm?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/a53ac989ce3ba1ecb6d283a57a2e91fc.mp4?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle with a colorful roster of <strong>eight</strong> commanders: from an <strong>Angry General</strong> to a <strong>Genius Chess Kid</strong>, a <strong>Goth Detective</strong> to a <strong>Retired Kingpin</strong>. Every leader brings a signature ability and a personality you won’t forget.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE ARSENAL → 20 Unique Units</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/ab1e65899b7a00436fb541e7facbdc12.poster.avif?t=1769509588\" width=1170 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/ab1e65899b7a00436fb541e7facbdc12.webm?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/ab1e65899b7a00436fb541e7facbdc12.mp4?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deploy <strong>20 Units</strong>, each with its own abilities and tactical strategies. From <strong>Standard troops </strong>to <strong>heavy machines</strong>, even quirky units like <strong>Magnets</strong>, <strong>Drills and Lasers,</strong> every unit has a role to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE WORLD → 8 Biomes, Endless Combinations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/c21bac453f7cd17106d5614a24e1e46a.poster.avif?t=1769509588\" width=1170 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/c21bac453f7cd17106d5614a24e1e46a.webm?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/c21bac453f7cd17106d5614a24e1e46a.mp4?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle across <strong>eight distinct biomes</strong>, freely mixed to form unique maps. Each biome offers its own tiles and special tiles: some protect, some heal, some break under your feet! Positioning matters as much as the units you deploy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE EDITOR → Build Your Battleground</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/bb7c284e8d46c473cb770dad42d01fa9.poster.avif?t=1769509588\" width=1170 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/bb7c284e8d46c473cb770dad42d01fa9.webm?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172160/extras/bb7c284e8d46c473cb770dad42d01fa9.mp4?t=1769509588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your own arenas using the full map creator. Mix biomes, shape terrain, craft clever layouts, and share your creations with the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you seize the moment and claim Atlantis?<br>The adventure awaits.<br> <i><strong>Avante to glory!</strong></i></p>",
